    ### About This Application

    Like most Node.js web applications, this one relies on a number of smaller modules installed via [npm](http://npmjs.org) to handle HTTP requests and store data. The key modules for this application are:

    * [`express`](http://expressjs.com) - a popular web framework that helps us respond to HTTP requests to our application.
    * [`mongoose`](http://mongoosejs.com/) - an Object/Document Mapper (ODM) for [MongoDB](http://www.mongodb.org/).
    * [`twilio`](https://twilio.github.io/twilio-node) - the Twilio Node module will help us generate TwiML responses to drive our interview.

